                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.34119/535: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cox</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-08-08T12:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 8, 1936—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>103. For Braden. Your 157, August 7, 9 p.m. The Department approves the procedure
                    outlined in your telegram under reference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
